// `@comptime` declarations forming a dep cycle — TS emits C4009 on the
// cycle. Vader's codes.vader assigns C4001 to DependencyCycle, so the
// diag-parity surface shows the same situation as TS-C4009 vs Vader-C4001.
module "snippet"

@comptime
export A :: B + 1

@comptime
export B :: A + 1

main :: fn() -> i32 {
    return A
}
